ji\" /><br />\n<br />\nAdmin工作就算9數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n能力包括（eg Top sales, 超強project management 奇難雜症都搞得掂, 極專業既technical skill 其他人想學都唔係咁易學到）括號入面是旦中一樣都得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T03:25:06.000Z","msg":"對巴打既經歷好有興趣<br />\n巴打你係唔係做開sales b2b / project management? <br />\n完全睇通職場點work<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我家陣都好努力develop problem solving skill，要再多加訓練下先有火力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b60340746a318fb913b58feb64709769b1eee406","tid":1167701,"uid":245803,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a928ea37e6d93dfaa348c0cad39821ef328ec101","tid":1167701,"uid":229095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T08:14:08.000Z","msg":"入行唔轉<br />\n轉第二份都係差唔多人工同待遇<br />\n但係而家個份冇野學<br />\n只係係到做打雜<br />\n日日返工唔知自己做緊咩<br />\n冇晒目標<br />\n點樣可以真係的起心肝去搵另一份？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T03:27:01.000Z","msg":"老細太9 所以宜家轉咗"},{"pid":"bc1e0f90aa86befb88dc6bf6a52891b17fd8daed","tid":1167701,"uid":232126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T15:19:39.000Z","msg":"等到有雙糧就有勇氣轉"},{"pid":"0754d47a1a880c86401b3b76d086144c13c54d3a","tid":1167701,"uid":50801,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T15:27:39.000Z","msg":"轉工唔洗勇氣，只要你諗下而家既工作模式維持多十年你頂唔頂到，頂唔順就要走人<br />\n再唔係簡單d，每日起身你係咩反應？<br />\n係覺得&ldquo;唉，夠鐘出門返工&rdquo;定係&ldquo;嘩屌，我受夠啦，我唔返啦&rdquo;<br />\n如果係第二種反應，你應該搵過份<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c22a939b5c3a9fa4c82882aa8c3220fa023b3eb","tid":1167701,"uid":126005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T15:32:17.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"5b42c0535e6fec125f121d1119afd67abf93225d","tid":1167701,"uid":111271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T15:40:01.000Z","msg":"同樓主一樣 返工無野學  部門仲要得自己一個<br />\n99%時間無野做 光明正大上連登  人工低<br />\n返左一個月已經想走 但又的唔起心肝走"},{"pid":"da6e3ec11573a4c75f30fe896c90